sections.heading: motor cars; failure to equip; violation; penalty
sections.text: Any railroad which uses or permits to be used on its line in this state a track motor car in violation of section 74-592 shall be guilty of a Class V misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1949, c. 217, ยง 2, p. 616;Laws 1977, LB 39, ยง 185;Laws 1994, LB 414, ยง 9.
